            "title": "財經｜本港失業率升至3.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"財經｜本港失業率升至3.9%\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mDioGulK3l3cDkpfs1VHUw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ca/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜本港失業率升至3.9%</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政府統計處公布，本港去年11月至今年1月經季節性調整失業率升至3.9%，較去年10月至12月的3.8%，升0.1個百分點；就業不足率維持1.7%。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%87%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B33-9-084208994.html",
